<div class="restaurant">
  <div class="container">

  <%= render partial: 'layouts/restaurantcarousel' %>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
          <h3>Find a Recipe For Ingredients You Already Have</h3>
          <p>Do you need help finding recipes to cook with the ingredients that are in you already have? Checkout our recipe generator. Simply type in the ingredients you have in you house that you want to cook with and we will give you some recipe ideas.</p>
          <br><%= render 'form' %><br>
          <button type="button" id="add-more">Add up to 5 ingredients!</button>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
          <h3>Don't Throw Away Your Food</h3>
          <p>Did you know that there are many food items that can have second lives, even after they look like they should be thrown away? Here are some great ideas for how to easily save your food from the compost and repurposed it into new uses that'll make you (and your wallet) glad you didn't throw them away.</p>
          <%= link_to "Why Youâ€™ll Never Again Throw Away Vegetable Peels", "http://www.thekitchn.com/why-youll-never-again-throw-away-vegetable-peels-waste-not-219967" %>
        </div>
     </div>

    <div class="container">
      <% if @recipe_info == [] %>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4>Sorry, your list of ingredients did not turn up with any recipes! Please try again with other ingredients.</h4>
        </div>
      <% elsif @recipe_info != nil %>


        <div class="restaurant">
          <div class="row">

            <% @recipe_info.each do |recipe_hash| %>
              <div class="block-heading-two">
                <h3><span class="color"><%= recipe_hash[:name] %> | <%= link_to "Get Recipe", recipe_hash[:link] %></span></h3>
              </div>
              <%= image_tag "#{recipe_hash[:image]}", class: "img-responsive img-thumbnail", style: "width: 150px; height: 150px;" %>
              <div class="container">

              <div class="item-ingred">
                <h4>Ingredient List: </h4>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <% recipe_hash[:ingredient].each do |ing| %>
                  <li><%= ing %></li>
                <% end %>
                </ul>
              </div>
            <% end %>

        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
